# Finja Weather API - Docker Ignore
#
# Defense in depth: the Dockerfile currently COPYs only the exact files it
# needs (requirements.txt, weather_api.py, providers.py) rather than
# `COPY . .`, so nothing here is actively exploitable today. This exists so
# a future Dockerfile change to a blanket COPY can't silently start baking
# secrets or test/dev files into the image.

__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
venv/
.git/
.gitignore
*.md

# Tests (never needed inside the running container)
test_*.py

# Test coverage artifacts
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/

# Secrets — never include in a Docker image!
.env
